title: Monoprice HDMI Right Angle Port Saver Adapter (Male to Female) - 270 Degree - Vertical Flat Right
description: Are tight spaces giving you a problem connecting your HDMI cable? Are you tired of having to move your equipment just to reach those hard-to-get-to places? Use an HDMI port saver to save time and efforts in your cable setup! Our HDMI port savers (male to female) give you the flexibility you need without risking bending your HDMI cables excessively which may damage the cable or even worse the ports on your expensive equipment. This port saver will help ease the strain at the point of connection to eliminate damage to the HDMI ports on your devices. This port saver supports 3D signals! If your port is vertically mounted and the flat side is on the left it would point upward
